Package PhotosView

Class PhotoDisplayController

  • java.lang.Object
    • PhotosView.PhotoDisplayController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class PhotoDisplayController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    UI controller in which the user selects a photo from one of their albums, and they can view the photo and change the photo details, such as tags and captions.
    Author:
    Eshan Wadhwa and Vishal Patel.
